111ua AKA Racing.  \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ua chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 Gi\u1ea3i \u0111ua xe vi\u1ec7t d\u00e3 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (AXCR \u2013 Asia Cross Country Rally) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Campuchia.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m \u00d4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2022 (VMS), Mitsubishi tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y m\u1eabu xe \u0111ua AKA Triton c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ua AKA Racing.  \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ua chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 Gi\u1ea3i \u0111ua xe vi\u1ec7t d\u00e3 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (AXCR \u2013 Asia Cross Country Rally) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Campuchia.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy lazy-blur\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_916_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454409_916_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_916_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_916_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_916_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_916_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_916_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc xe tham gia gi\u1ea3i \u0111ua \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 l\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u201c\u1ed1ng th\u1edf\u201d (\u1ed1ng h\u00fat gi\u00f3) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao, tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 khi l\u1ed9i s\u00f4ng su\u1ed1i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e1o r\u1eddi ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u xe v\u00e0 \u0111u\u00f4i xe, t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng khi xe sa l\u1ea7y.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfc xe tham gia gi\u1ea3i \u0111ua \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 l\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u201c\u1ed1ng th\u1edf\u201d (\u1ed1ng h\u00fat gi\u00f3) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng cao, tr\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 khi l\u1ed9i s\u00f4ng su\u1ed1i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e1o r\u1eddi ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u xe v\u00e0 \u0111u\u00f4i xe, t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng khi xe sa l\u1ea7y.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy lazy-blur\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_524_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454409_524_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_524_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-239x300.jpg 239w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_524_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x753.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_524_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 720w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C\u1ea7n g\u1ea1t n\u01b0\u1edbc cho xe Rally \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 b\u01a1m n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 phun n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 g\u1ea1t li\u00ean t\u1ee5c (xe b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ec3 phun n\u01b0\u1edbc).  V\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, tay \u0111ua kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ea1t c\u1ea7n g\u1ea1t n\u01b0\u1edbc li\u00ean t\u1ee5c n\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng t\u1eafc ri\u00eang n\u1eb1m b\u00ean ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 phun n\u01b0\u1edbc li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C\u1ea7n g\u1ea1t n\u01b0\u1edbc cho xe Rally \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 b\u01a1m n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 phun n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 g\u1ea1t li\u00ean t\u1ee5c (xe b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ec3 phun n\u01b0\u1edbc).  V\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, tay \u0111ua kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ea1t c\u1ea7n g\u1ea1t n\u01b0\u1edbc li\u00ean t\u1ee5c n\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng t\u1eafc ri\u00eang n\u1eb1m b\u00ean ph\u00eda ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 phun n\u01b0\u1edbc li\u00ean t\u1ee5c.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_436_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454409_436_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_436_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_436_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-1024x614.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_436_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_436_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_436_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ean c\u1ee7a l\u00e1i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 l\u00e1i c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m m\u00e1u tr\u00ean c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda.  Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean c\u1eeda xe, qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tay \u0111ua \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in t\u00ean, nh\u00f3m m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ec3 khi g\u1eb7p tai n\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi truy\u1ec1n m\u00e1u.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ean c\u1ee7a l\u00e1i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 l\u00e1i c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m m\u00e1u tr\u00ean c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda.  Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean c\u1eeda xe, qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tay \u0111ua \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c in t\u00ean, nh\u00f3m m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ec3 khi g\u1eb7p tai n\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi truy\u1ec1n m\u00e1u.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_359_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454409_359_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_359_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-227x300.jpg 227w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_359_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-775x1024.jpg 775w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_359_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-768x1015.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_359_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-1162x1536.jpg 1162w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_359_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x793.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_359_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tay \u0111ua c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y.  Khi \u0111eo th\u00eam g\u0103ng tay, gi\u00e0y, kh\u1ea9u trang s\u1ebd bao ph\u1ee7 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y n\u1ed5, k\u00ednh v\u1ee1, v\u1eadt th\u1ec3 bay\u2026 d\u00e2y \u0111ai \u1edf c\u1ea7u vai, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00e1m \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c nh\u1ea5c v\u00e0 k\u00e9o ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i ra kh\u1ecfi xe v\u00f9ng nguy hi\u1ec3m.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u00ean m\u0169 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 Intercom (li\u00ean l\u1ea1c n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9) bao g\u1ed3m mic v\u00e0 tai nghe, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 Intercom tr\u00ean xe, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c tay \u0111ua giao ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau v\u00ec tr\u00ean xe khi \u0111ua ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i.  R\u1ea5t \u1ed3n \u00e0o, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111ua WRC (World Rally Championshop) s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed1n s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi ch\u00e9p tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.  Trong Rally Cross s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u201ccu\u1ed1n s\u1ed5 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d ghi l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac cua, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.  Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i ph\u1ee5 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng ghi ch\u00fa n\u00e0y cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i ch\u00ednh.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tay \u0111ua c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y.  Khi \u0111eo th\u00eam g\u0103ng tay, gi\u00e0y, kh\u1ea9u trang s\u1ebd bao ph\u1ee7 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y n\u1ed5, k\u00ednh v\u1ee1, v\u1eadt th\u1ec3 bay\u2026 d\u00e2y \u0111ai \u1edf c\u1ea7u vai, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00e1m \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c nh\u1ea5c v\u00e0 k\u00e9o ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i ra kh\u1ecfi xe v\u00f9ng nguy hi\u1ec3m.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u00ean m\u0169 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 Intercom (li\u00ean l\u1ea1c n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9) bao g\u1ed3m mic v\u00e0 tai nghe, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 Intercom tr\u00ean xe, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c tay \u0111ua giao ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau v\u00ec tr\u00ean xe khi \u0111ua ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i.  R\u1ea5t \u1ed3n \u00e0o, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111ua WRC (World Rally Championshop) s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed1n s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi ch\u00e9p tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.  Trong Rally Cross s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u201ccu\u1ed1n s\u1ed5 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d ghi l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng kh\u00fac cua, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.  Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i ph\u1ee5 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng ghi ch\u00fa n\u00e0y cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i ch\u00ednh.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_357_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454409_357_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_357_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/