12.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_199_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_199_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">V\u00ec l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh k\u00edn n\u00ean chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111ua ph\u1ea3i mang theo r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.  C\u1ed1p xe tinh ch\u1ec9nh, c\u00f3 th\u00eam gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee1 l\u1ed1p.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">V\u00ec l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u1edf \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh k\u00edn n\u00ean chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111ua ph\u1ea3i mang theo r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.  C\u1ed1p xe tinh ch\u1ec9nh, c\u00f3 th\u00eam gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee1 l\u1ed1p.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_915_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454409_915_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_915_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_915_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_915_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_915_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_915_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3m x\u00f3c nguy\u00ean b\u1ea3n theo xe s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua n\u00ean 100% c\u00e1c xe \u0111ua \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 4 phu\u1ed9c cho 4 b\u00e1nh nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc Triton c\u1ee7a AKA Racing th\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p l\u00ean 8 phu\u1ed9c, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed7i b\u00e1nh c\u00f3 2 phu\u1ed9c, g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 phu\u1ed9c k\u00e9p.  \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 phu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u M\u1ef9 King Shock, gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam 135 tri\u1ec7u 1 b\u1ed9, 2 b\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n 300 tri\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3m x\u00f3c nguy\u00ean b\u1ea3n theo xe s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua n\u00ean 100% c\u00e1c xe \u0111ua \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 4 phu\u1ed9c cho 4 b\u00e1nh nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc Triton c\u1ee7a AKA Racing th\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p l\u00ean 8 phu\u1ed9c, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed7i b\u00e1nh c\u00f3 2 phu\u1ed9c, g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 phu\u1ed9c k\u00e9p.  \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 phu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u M\u1ef9 King Shock, gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam 135 tri\u1ec7u 1 b\u1ed9, 2 b\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n 300 tri\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_398_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454409_398_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_398_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_398_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_398_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_398_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_398_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a xe c\u0169ng kh\u00e1c b\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i b\u1edfi c\u00f3 th\u00eam h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng li\u00ean l\u1ea1c n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, gh\u1ebf \u00f4m s\u00e1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, d\u00e2y \u0111ai an to\u00e0n 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m (ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u1ea5n n\u00fat l\u00e0 m\u1edf)\u2026 v\u00e0 l\u1ed3ng l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng th\u00e9p h\u00ecnh \u1ed1ng.  T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a l\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tay l\u00e1i n\u1ebfu xe b\u1ecb l\u1eadt (l\u1ed3ng l\u1eadt).<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a l\u1ed3ng cu\u1ed9n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ti\u1ebft b\u1edfi FIA (Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n \u00f4 t\u00f4 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf).  V\u00ed d\u1ee5: trong Rally Cross, v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 \u1ed1ng th\u00e9p c\u00e1n ngu\u1ed9i li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p kim, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u1ed1ng th\u00e9p \u0111\u00fac v\u00e0 cho c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi \u1ed1ng th\u00e9p h\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.  \u0110\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a \u1ed1ng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 350 N\/m2 vu\u00f4ng g\u00f3c v\u1edbi b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">V\u1ec1 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u00e1c \u1ed1ng ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u1ed1ng l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y cao nh\u01b0 D45 x 2,5 mm (\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00ednh 45 mm, d\u00e0y 2,5 mm) ho\u1eb7c D50 x 2 mm, c\u00e1c \u1ed1ng ph\u1ee5 s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1ed1ng D38 x 2,5 mm ho\u1eb7c D40 x 2 mm .<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t xe c\u0169ng kh\u00e1c b\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i b\u1edfi c\u00f3 th\u00eam h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng li\u00ean l\u1ea1c n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, gh\u1ebf \u00f4m s\u00e1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi, d\u00e2y \u0111ai an to\u00e0n 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m (ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u1ea5n n\u00fat l\u00e0 m\u1edf)\u2026 v\u00e0 l\u1ed3ng l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng th\u00e9p h\u00ecnh \u1ed1ng.  T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a l\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tay l\u00e1i n\u1ebfu xe b\u1ecb l\u1eadt (l\u1ed3ng l\u1eadt).<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a l\u1ed3ng cu\u1ed9n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ti\u1ebft b\u1edfi FIA (Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n \u00f4 t\u00f4 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf).  V\u00ed d\u1ee5 trong Rally Cross, v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 \u1ed1ng th\u00e9p c\u00e1n ngu\u1ed9i li\u1ec1n m\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p kim, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u1ed1ng th\u00e9p \u0111\u00fac v\u00e0 cho \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi \u1ed1ng th\u00e9p h\u00e0n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n k\u00e9m h\u01a1n.  \u0110\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a \u1ed1ng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 350 N\/m2 vu\u00f4ng g\u00f3c v\u1edbi b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">V\u1ec1 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u00e1c \u1ed1ng ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u1ed1ng l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y cao nh\u01b0 D45 x 2,5 mm (\u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00ednh 45 mm, d\u00e0y 2,5 mm) ho\u1eb7c D50 x 2 mm, c\u00e1c \u1ed1ng ph\u1ee5 s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1ed1ng D38 x 2,5 mm ho\u1eb7c D40 x 2 mm .<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_576_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454409_576_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_576_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-300x190.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_576_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-1024x647.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_576_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-768x485.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_576_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x379.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454409_576_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C\u00f4ng t\u1eafc m\u00e0u n\u00e2u l\u00e0 Emergency Stop, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a FIA \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eaft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7n k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 m\u00e1y ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1.  V\u00ec n\u1ebfu t\u1eaft m\u00e1y ph\u00e1t m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 v\u1eabn ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eaft \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1edbi cho xe d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.  N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1eaft k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i b\u00ean trong xe, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u00e2y b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1eaft k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u00ean n\u1eafp ca-p\u00f4 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng t\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p t\u00e0i x\u1ebf ng\u1ea5t x\u1ec9u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ng\u1eaft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ch\u1eadp ch\u00e1y.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C\u00f4ng t\u1eafc m\u00e0u n\u00e2u l\u00e0 Emergency Stop, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a FIA \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eaft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7n k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 m\u00e1y ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1.  V\u00ec n\u1ebfu t\u1eaft m\u00e1y ph\u00e1t m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 v\u1eabn ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eaft \u0111i\u1ec7n m\u1edbi cho xe d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.  N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1eaft k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i b\u00ean trong xe, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u00e2y b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1eaft k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u00ean n\u1eafp ca-p\u00f4 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng t\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p t\u00e0i x\u1ebf ng\u1ea5t x\u1ec9u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ng\u1eaft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh ch\u1eadp ch\u00e1y.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_770_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454410_770_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_770_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_770_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-1024x678.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_770_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-768x508.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_770_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x397.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_770_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Khi \u0111ua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 r\u1ea3nh tay \u0111\u1ec3 u\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00ecnh n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1eafn ph\u00eda sau xe, n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u1ed1ng, ph\u00eda tr\u00ean c\u00f3 van c\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00fat n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb \u1ed1ng. <\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, xe c\u00f2n c\u00f3 b\u00faa ph\u00e1 k\u00ednh, b\u00ecnh ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y mini ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Khi \u0111ua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 r\u1ea3nh tay \u0111\u1ec3 u\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00ecnh n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1eafn ph\u00eda sau xe, n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u1ed1ng, ph\u00eda tr\u00ean c\u00f3 van c\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00fat n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eeb \u1ed1ng. <\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, xe c\u00f2n c\u00f3 b\u00faa ph\u00e1 k\u00ednh, b\u00ecnh ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y mini ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_176_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg\" title=\"1672454410_176_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_176_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_176_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_176_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_176_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454410_176_diem-dac-biet-tren-chiec-xe-triton-cua-doi-dua.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9i \u0111ua AKA Racing c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 hai chi\u1ebfc Triton tham gia gi\u1ea3i AXCR t\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Campuchia, t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 21 \u0111\u1ebfn 26 th\u00e1ng 11.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9i \u0111ua AKA Racing c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 hai chi\u1ebfc Triton tham gia gi\u1ea3i AXCR t\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Campuchia, t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 21 \u0111\u1ebfn 26 th\u00e1ng 11.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng phu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay, \u1ed1ng l\u1ed3ng ch\u1ed1ng l\u1eadt hay c\u00f4ng t\u1eafc kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc b\u00e1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. Trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m \u00d4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2022 (VMS), Mitsubishi tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y m\u1eabu xe \u0111ua AKA Triton c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ua AKA Racing. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":15262,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15261"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[